argus-gsi-pep-callout 1.3.1
---------------------------
* Implements a caching mechanism of the authorized identity (username)
  for GSI OpenSSH which calls to gsi-pep-callout twice (first authN then authZ)
  https://savannah.cern.ch/bugs/index.php?101032
* Library version-info 1:1:0

argus-gsi-pep-callout 1.3.0
---------------------------
* Packaging moved to separate projects.

argus-gsi-pep-callout 1.2.3
---------------------------
* Self managed packaging with spec file for RPM generation.
* Self managed packaging with Debian control files.

argus-gsi-pep-callout 1.2.2
---------------------------
* New version number for EMI-2 release.

argus-gsi-pep-callout 1.2.1
---------------------------
* callout function renamed to argus_pep_callout.
* library version-info 1:0:0
* Bug fix: https://savannah.cern.ch/bugs/index.php?79412
* Bug fix: correctly read the X.509 PEM cert chain.

argus-gsi-pep-callout 1.2.0
---------------------------
* Uses new thread-safe Argus PEP client library (pep-api-c)
* xacml_profileid configuration parameter added.

glite-authz-gsi-pep-callout 1.1.1
---------------------------------
* Copyright updated in sources.

glite-authz-gsi-pep-callout 1.1.0
---------------------------------
* Compatible with Argus 1.1 services.
* Implements XACML Grid WN Authorization Profile v.1.0.
* Security and source code review recommendations implemented.
* xacml_actionid configuration parameter added.
* TLS/SSL configuration parameters udpated with default values.

glite-authz-gsi-pep-callout 1.0.0
---------------------------------
* Initial release of the gridftp GSI PEP callout plugin.
